scene.message:
Mark: Who the hell are you?!{nl}
You locked me in here!{nl}
You're gonna pay!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey, cool it Mark!{nl}
You'll tick him off!{nl}
Better butter him up...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: There you are!{nl}
Inaba! Are you okay?{waitkey}{clearbox}...Wait,{nl}
Brown's here too?!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You bastard Nanjo!{nl}
What took you so long?!{nl}
...{wait_fr:32}...{wait_fr:32}...{wait_fr:48}Sonoda?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Oh, it's just you{nl}
guys...{wait_fr:37} So you missed{nl}
me that much?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Hey Brown,{nl}
why were you trying to{nl}
butter him up?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: You've got the wrong{nl}
people — we're on your side.{nl}
No need to butter us up.{waitkey}Lucky you, Brown?{waitkey}{clearbox}...More importantly,{nl}
why are you here?{nl}
I thought only Inaba{nl}
was captured.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I figured I needed{nl}
weapons to fight demons,{nl}
so I came here.{waitkey}Then I ended up{nl}
getting caught with Mark!{waitkey}{clearbox}What a disaster...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Shut it, Brown!{waitkey}{clearbox}...Sonoda!{nl}
What are you doing here?{waitkey}And more importantly —{nl}
you doing okay{nl}
out here?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Not this again!{nl}
Come on, I keep saying{nl}
I'm totally fine!{waitkey}{ret}

Inspector: ...{wait_fr:21}Inaba, don't{nl}
go outside without{nl}
permission.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Inspector!{nl}
Even as a joke, that's a{nl}
bit much! I did nothing!{waitkey}{ret}

Officer: Inspector, he{nl}
escaped! He's a dangerous{nl}
criminal!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: There's a foul{nl}
smell...{wait_fr:21}{nl}
Don't tell me...!!{waitkey}{ret}

Demon Officer: Death penalty!{nl}
Death penalty!{nl}
Die die die die die!{nl}
Ehehehehe!{waitkey}{ret}

Demon Inspector: That's right!{nl}
You guys —{nl}
get 'em!{waitkey}{ret}
